in%20the%2012th%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20opened%20India's%20medal%20tally%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Olympics%20after%20she%20secured%20third%20place%20in%20the%20women's%20individual%2010m%20Air%20pistol%20event.%20Following%20that%2C%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20and%20Bhaker%20won%20the%20Bronze%20medal%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20(mixed%20team)%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20a%20shot%20at%20returning%20with%20three%20medals%20from%20Paris.%20But%20in%20her%20final%20event%2C%20she%20narrowly%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20historic%20grand%20treble%20and%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20women's%2025m%20pistol%20shooting%20event.%20She%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20opportunity%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20three%20medals%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20is%20the%20first%20athlete%20from%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20after%20independence%20to%20get%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%201900%20Olympics%2C%20Norman%20Pritchard%20won%20two%20medals%20while%20representing%20India%2C%20both%20silver%20in%20the%20200m%20and%20200m%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20also%20joined%20an%20elite%20group%20of%20athletes%20to%20have%20multiple%20individual%20medals%20at%20the%20Olympics%3A%20PV%20Sindhu%20(badminton%20silver%20at%20Rio%202016%20and%20bronze%20medal%20at%20Tokyo%202020)%20and%20Sushil%20Kumar%20(wrestling%20bronze%20at%20the%202008%20Beijing%20Olympics%20and%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Olympics).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722742380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcufs38lg_manu-bhaker-flag-afp_625x300_04_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2F