ael-conflict-gaza-war-hezbollah-hamas-fears-of-all-out-war-grow-in-middle-east-as-iran-israel-conflict-widens-6258750%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singapore%20tourist%20shares%20'ugly'%20rickshaw%20experience%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722738676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112257407%2Cimgsize-1099057.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwe-got-scammed-in-old-delhi-singapore-tourist-shares-ugly-rickshaw-experience%2Farticleshow%2F112257320.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Singaporean%20travel%20vlogger%20shared%20an%20incident%20with%20a%20Delhi%20rickshaw%20driver%20who%20initially%20agreed%20to%20a%20fare%20of%20Rs100%20but%20later%20demanded%20Rs6%2C000%20and%20left%20them%20stranded.%20The%20driver%20had%20made%20multiple%20unwanted%20stops%20and%20led%20them%20to%20a%20store%20despite%20their%20wish%20to%20explore%20independently%2C%20raising%20concerns%20over%20tourist%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwe-got-scammed-in-old-delhi-singapore-tourist-shares-ugly-rickshaw-experience%2Farticleshow%2F112257320.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTried%20To%20Act%20Sportsmanlike%26quot%3B%3A%20Imane%20Khelif's%20Opponent%20After%20Olympics%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bout%20that%20attracted%20global%20attention%2C%20Hungary's%20Luca%20Anna%20Hamori%20(66kg)%20braved%20intimidating%20gender%20row%20boxer%20Iman%20Khelif%20for%20three%20competitive%20rounds%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20and%20walked%20out%20feeling%20proud%20of%20herself%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20fighting%20was%20not%20an%20option%26quot%3B%20for%20her%2C%20here%20Saturday.%20The%20Algerian%2C%20embroiled%20in%20a%20major%20gender%20controversy%20in%20the%20French%20capital%2C%20left%20the%20ring%20in%20tears%20after%20she%20guaranteed%20herself%20at%20least%20bronze%20by%20entering%20the%20women's%2066kg%20semifinals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20previous%20opponent%2C%20Italian%20boxer%20Angela%20Carini%20had%20pulled%20out%20of%20her%20bout%20against%20Khelif%20on%20Thursday%20just%20after%2046%20seconds%2C%20unable%20to%20take%20heavy%20punches%20from%20the%20Algerian%2C%20who%20was%20banned%20from%20the%202023%20World%20Championship%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20failing%20the%20gender%20eligibility%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20turn%20of%20events%20had%20created%20a%20huge%20furore%20in%20the%20boxing%20world%20and%20at%20the%20Games%2C%20with%20many%20questioning%20Khelif's%20presence%20in%20the%20women's%20competition%20even%20as%20IOC%20put%20up%20a%20stout%20defence%20of%20their%20decision%20to%20allow%20the%20Algerian%20to%20compete%20as%20a%20female.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuca%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20she%20won't%20step%20back%20and%20she%20kept%20her%20promise%20with%20a%20courageous%20show.%20She%20took%20several%20punches%20on%20her%20body%20and%20also%20succeeded%20in%20landing%20a%20few%20on%20her%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Khelif%2C%20who%20was%20cheered%20by%20the%20crowd%2C%20emerged%20victorious%2C%20taking%20a%205-0%20unanimous%20decision%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarini%20had%20refused%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20Khelif%20and%20later%20regretted%20the%20decision%20but%20Luca%20showed%20respect%20to%20the%20Algerian%20and%20even%20hugged%20her.%20Returning%20the%20gesture%2C%20Khelif%20held%20the%20ropes%20for%20Luca%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20hard%20fight%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I%20could%20do%20everything%20what%20I%20wanted%20before%20the%20fight.%20And%20I%20think%20it%20was%20a%20good%20fight.%20I'm%20so%20proud%20of%20myself%20and%20I'm%20so%20grateful%20to%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Luca%20said%2C%20addressing%20a%20herd%20of%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20able%20to%20enjoy%203x3%20minutes%20continuously%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20disappointed%20for%20a%20moment.%20This%20is%20how%20it%20is%20now%2C%20but%20who%20knows%20what%20the%20future%20holds.%20I%20tried%20to%20act%20sportsmanlike%2C%20so%20that%20my%20opponent%20couldn't%20say%20anything%20bad%20about%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Hungarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%20walked%20through%20the%20mixed%20zone%2C%20still%20wiping%20her%20tears%20but%20did%20not%20speak%20with%20the%20waiting%20print%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20these%20past%20few%20days%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20everyone%2C%20both%20for%20him%20(sic)%20and%20for%20me%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20that%20I%20respect%20him%20(sic)%2C%20and%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20bad%20opinion%20about%20him%2C%20because%20that's%20not%20him.%26quot%3B%20Luca%20spoke%20flanked%20by%20Zsolt%20Gyulai%2C%20the%20two-time%20Olympic%20champion%20and%20President%20of%20Hungary%20Olympic%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalazs%20F%C3%BAri%C3%A1s%2C%20the%20IOC%20member%20from%20Hungary%2C%20said%20not%20entering%20the%20ring%20was%20not%20an%20option%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20every%20match%20is%20decided%20on%20the%20play%20field%20and%20not%20elsewhere.%20So%20we%20are%20absolutely%20convinced%2C%20100%25%20convinced%2C%20that%20every%20match%20has%20to%20be%20decided%20on%20the%20play%20field%2C%20this%20time%2C%20this%20case%2C%20in%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20it%20was%20never%20an%20option%2C%20neither%20for%20Luca.%20We%20couldn't%20have%20even%20convinced%20her%2C%20neither%20the%20president%2C%20nor%20myself%2C%20nor%20the%20whole%20Olympic%20committee%2C%20not%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20always%20wanted%20to%20fight%2C%20and%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20what%20I%20have%20said%20before%2C%20it%20was