p%3EIsraeli%20defence%20officials%20say%20they%20are%20coordinating%20with%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20strike%20by%20Iran%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20repeat%20of%20a%20similar%20attack%20by%20Tehran%20in%20April%20that%20was%20repelled%20by%20allies.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIsraeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Friday%20that%20he%20spoke%20with%20his%20American%20and%20British%20counterparts%2C%20Lloyd%20Austin%20and%20John%20Healey%2C%20and%20provided%20%26quot%3Ba%20situational%20assessment%20in%20light%20of%20recent%20security%20developments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFear%20has%20risen%20of%20a%20spillover%20from%20the%20nearly%2010-month%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20in%20Gaza%20as%20Iran%20threatened%20retaliation%20for%20the%20assassination%20in%20Tehran%20this%20week%20of%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20the%20political%20leader%20of%20the%20Iran-backed%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20spike%20in%20tensions%20about%20four%20months%20ago%20saw%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20trade%20direct%20fire%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Almost%20300%20Iranian%20drones%20and%20missiles%20were%20fired%20but%20most%20were%20destroyed%20by%20air%20defences%20from%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20and%20several%20allies.%20Israel's%20drone%20strike%20in%20response%20was%20contained%20and%20appeared%20symbolic%20to%20avoid%20escalation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Iran's%20response%20may%20be%20more%20fierce%2C%20given%20the%20embarrassment%20of%20having%20a%20foreign%20dignitary%20and%20top%20ally%20assassinated%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20capital.%20Among%20its%20options%20are%20another%20direct%20assault%20on%20Israel%2C%20stepped-up%20attacks%20by%20its%20proxies%20in%20the%20region%20or%20hitting%20Israeli%20targets%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustin%2C%20who%20earlier%20this%20week%20reiterated%20that%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20will%20help%20defend%20Israel%26quot%3B%20if%20attacked%2C%20spoke%20with%20Gallant%20and%20is%20weighing%20moves%20to%20reinforce%20America's%20presence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20Friday.%20White%20House%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%20earlier%20in%20a%20CNN%20interview%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20is%20ensuring%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20resources%20and%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20both%20equipment%20and%20personnel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Very%20Direct'%20Call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20stopped%20short%20of%20confirming%20it%20was%20behind%20killing%20Haniyeh%2C%20but%20it%20hasn't%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20claim%20either.%20His%20death%20also%20came%20hours%20after%20Israel%20killed%20a%20top%20Hezbollah%20commander%20in%20Beirut%2C%20Fuad%20Shukr.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Thursday%20assured%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20of%20%26quot%3Bnew%20defensive%20US%20military%20deployments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20Biden%20later%20told%20reporters%20he%20also%20pressed%20the%20Israeli%20leader%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20direct%26quot%3B%20call%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20is%20trying%20to%20use%20his%20last%20months%20in%20office%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20huge%20political%20divisions%20in%20the%20US.%20He's%20struggled%20to%20influence%20Netanyahu's%20war%20strategy%2C%20seeking%20to%20pressure%20him%20publicly%20and%20privately%20but%20declining%20to%20use%20as%20leverage%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20US%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeeting%20with%20senior%20leaders%20across%20the%20region%2C%20including%20today%20in%20Israel%2C%20we%20urged%20all%20sides%20to%20show%20restraint%20and%20dial%20down%20the%20tension%20at%20this%20critical%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20UK's%20Healey%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20need%20to%20see%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire%2C%20hostages%20released%20and%20aid%20getting%20in%20in%20sufficient%20quantity%20to%20alleviate%20the%20suffering%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Abraham%20Alliance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20destruction%20and%20death%20count%20among%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20has%20drawn%20international%20criticism%20of%20Israel%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20focused%20on%20the%20existential%20threat%20to%20his%20country%20and%20the%20region%20from%20Iran%20and%20its%20proxies%20in%20the%20so-called%20Axis%20of%20Resistance%2C%20which%20includes%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20both%20designated%20terrorist%20organizations%20by%20the%20US%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20referred%20to%20the%20coordinated%20April%20defence%20in%20a%20controversial%20speech%20last%20week%20to%20a%20joint%20meeting%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20possible%20template%20for%20a%20NATO-accord%20he%20termed%20the%20%26quot%3BAbraham%20Alliance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGallant%20in%20his%20statement%20Friday%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bemphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20establishing%20a%20coalition%20in%20Israel's%20defence%20against%20Iran's%20proxies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722735360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fln9sms9o_israel-army_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-iran-strike-looms-israel-hopes-for-abraham-alliance-with-us-uk-6258649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20defence%20officials%20say%20they%20are%20coordinating%20with%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20ahead%20of%20an%20exp