21-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20and%20simulate%20brain%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musk%20hopes%20the%20technology%20in%20the%20near%20future%20could%20heal%20neurological%20disorders%20or%20improve%20natural%20senses%20like%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20give%20people%20superpowers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20podcast%20interview%20with%20computer%20scientist%20Lex%20Friedman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-elon-musk-microchips-brains-ai-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembedded%20a%20Neuralink%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20brain%20of%20its%20first%20patient%20in%20January%202024.%20Weeks%20later%2C%20the%20company%20said%20the%20patient%20was%20able%20to%20control%20a%20computer%20mouse%20using%20just%20their%20thoughts.%20Musk%20said%20the%20company%20has%20since%20embedded%20a%20chip%20into%20a%20second%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20billed%20Neuralink%20as%20a%20technology%20that%2C%20in%20the%20future%2C%20could%20facilitate%20%26quot%3Bsymbiosis%26quot%3B%20between%20humans%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20In%20his%20conversation%20with%20Friedman%2C%20Musk%20said%20Neuralink%20chips%20could%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20AI%20from%20surpassing%20humans%20and%20going%20off%20the%20rails%20all%20%26quot%3BTerminator%26quot%3B%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20idea%20that%20may%20help%20with%20AI%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20better%20align%20collective%20human%20will%20with%20AI%20if%20the%20output%20rate%20especially%20was%20dramatically%20increased.%20And%20I%20think%20there's%20potential%20to%20increase%20the%20output%20rate%20by%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20three%2C%20maybe%20six%2C%20maybe%20more%20orders%20of%20magnitude.%20So%2C%20it's%20better%20than%20the%20current%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20are%20in%20a%20race%20to%20develop%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20which%20is%20a%20theoretical%20future%20technology%20in%20which%20AI%20can%20reason%20like%20humans.%20The%20idea%20has%20been%20met%20with%20no%20small%20amount%20of%20concern.%20Musk%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-elon-musk-and-sam-altman-relationship-feuds-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20criticized%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20leading%20AI%20company%2C%20which%20he%20helped%20found%2C%20for%20being%20too%20aggressive%20and%20not%20adequately%20considering%20the%20importance%20of%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b70d92ee-3bd1-4382-8aff-d66a8f5bef68%5C%22%3EThe%20possibilities%20of%20Neuralink%20to%20improve%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20Neuralink%20devices%20will%20eventually%20be%20able%20to%20repair%20damaged%20neurons%20to%20help%20people%20with%20issues%20like%20blindness%20and%20paralysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20also%20solve%2C%20probably%2C%20schizophrenia%20if%20people%20have%20seizures%20of%20some%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20probably%20solve%20that.%20It%20could%20help%20with%20memory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Neuralink's%20aim%20isn't%20just%20to%20give%20people%20with%20neurological%20damage%20a%20full%20range%20of%20communication%20but%20to%20enhance%20their%20already%20natural%20abilities.%20He%20even%20suggested%20that%20a%20person%20using%20Neuralink%20might%20eventually%20have%20vision%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20resolution%20than%20human%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we're%20in%20there%2C%20why%20not%3F%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20compared%20vision%20enhancements%20with%20Neuralink%20to%20the%20visor%20worn%20by%20the%20character%20Geordi%20La%20Forge%20from%20Star%20Trek.%20La%20Forge%20wore%20a%20thin%20visor%20over%20his%20eyes%20that%20allowed%20him%20to%20see%20by%20reading%20the%20electromagnetic%20field%20and%20sending%20inputs%20to%20his%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20to%20see%20it%20in%20radar%3F%20No%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20see%20ultraviolet%2C%20infrared%2C%20eagle%20vision%2C%20whatever%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20solving%20issues%20like%20neuron%20damage%20is%20the%20first%20%26quot%3Bbaby%20step%26quot%3B%20to%20getting%20Neuralink%20to%20a%20point%20where%20it%20can%20do%20more%20complex%20things%20like%20communicating%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-help-humans-compete-with-ai-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722718062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ae871ba5247369a3e95721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-help-humans-compete-with-ai-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20says%20Neuralink%2C%20his%20venture%20into%20brain%20microchips%2C%20could%20allow%20humans%20to%20integrate%20with%20machines%2C%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3142%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-help-humans-compete-with-ai-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%20beats%20handicapped%20driver%20to%20death%20after%20auto%20grazes%20his%20SUV%20in%20Faridabad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722718043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112257394%2Cimgsize-26722.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Ffaridabad%2F