in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20observations.%20Even%20today%2C%20we%20get%20to%20see%20Dalit%20grooms%20being%20stopped%20from%20getting%20on%20a%20horse.%20Even%20educated%20Scheduled%20Caste%20people%20coming%20from%20well-to-do%20families%20face%20untouchability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20handle%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mr%20Paswan's%20father%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20who%20was%20a%20notable%20Dalit%20leader%2C%20and%20requested%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20reconsider%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20on%20reservation%20in%20sub-categories%20for%20SC-ST%20categories.%20The%20party's%20founder%20Padma%20Bhushan%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20ji%20has%20also%20been%20demanding%20that%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20a%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20against%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20the%20society%2C%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20provision%20for%20reservation%20in%20sub-categories%20and%20creamy%20layer%20for%20SC-ST%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20urges%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20reconsider%20the%20decision%20so%20that%20discrimination%20does%20not%20arise%20in%20the%20SC-ST%20society%20and%20society%20cannot%20be%20weakened%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20its%20verdict%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20seven-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20had%20said%20in%20its%20majority%20judgment%20that%20sub-classification%20is%20permitted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20members%20of%20SC%2FST%20categories%20are%20often%20unable%20to%20climb%20up%20the%20ladder%20due%20to%20the%20systemic%20discrimination%20they%20face.%20Article%2014%20permits%20sub-classification%20of%20caste...%20Historical%20and%20empirical%20evidence%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20are%20a%20socially%20heterogeneous%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20sub-classification%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs%20as%20not%20doing%20so%20perpetuates%20inequality%20within%20the%20reserved%20categories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Census%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Paswan%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20caste%20census%20demand%2C%20which%20has%20also%20become%20a%20topic%20of%20heated%20discussion%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Parliament%20session%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20it%20for%20framing%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20should%20have%20a%20caste%20census.%20But%20its%20findings%20must%20not%20be%20made%20public.%20The%20data%20should%20be%20used%20by%20the%20government%20for%20framing%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722702000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6lp4c8ng_chirag-paswan_625x300_30_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-sc-st-sub-classification-on-supreme-courts-sc-st-sub-classification-order-bjp-allys-big-declaration-6256543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20said%20his%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20will%20appeal%20against%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20allowing%20sub-classification%20within%20the%20reservation%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-sc-st-sub-classification-on-supreme-courts-sc-st-