0rewarded%20for%20our%20efforts%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftorre-guinigi-italian-tower-photos-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estunning%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20leisurely%20lunches%20at%20local%20restaurants.%20By%20arriving%20at%20restaurants%20when%20they%20opened%20for%20lunch%2C%20we%20never%20had%20trouble%20getting%20a%20table%20big%20enough%20for%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20breakfast%20and%20dinner%20at%20our%20rental%2C%20which%20meant%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-far-to-shop-lidl-italy-best-things-to-buy-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrips%20to%20the%20supermarket%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20saved%20us%20money%20and%20allowed%20us%20to%20try%20local%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreakfast%20was%20serve%20yourself%20and%20clean%20up%20after%20yourself%2C%20which%20worked.%20Dinner%20was%20done%20on%20a%20rotation%2C%20as%20was%20setting%20the%20table%20and%20cleaning%20up.%20Dinner%20at%20home%20made%20for%20much%20more%20relaxed%20dinners.%20No%20one%20had%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20they%20drank%20or%20about%20driving%20home%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20side%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20road%20on%20poor%20roads%20with%20no%20street%20lighting.%20We%20had%20a%20big%20outdoor%20setting%2C%20and%20we%20had%20slow%20dinners%20and%20chatted.%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20played%20family%20quizzes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20couple%20of%20nights%2C%20we%20went%20indoors%20after%20dinner%20and%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20movie%26quot%3B%20night.%20One%20night%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3BGladiator.%26quot%3B%20Most%20of%20us%20had%20seen%20it%2C%20but%20it%20was%20fun%20to%20watch%20it%20together%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20laughed%2C%20we%20ate%2C%20we%20drank%2C%20we%20played%20games%2C%20we%20swam%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20divine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218c1a9ae-e20c-46d7-bcdc-426b7ad8510c%5C%22%3EIt%20wasn't%20perfect%2C%20but%20it%20was%20absolutely%20worth%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20so%20worth%20traveling%20with%20our%20adult%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Kiddults%20as%20we%20sometimes%20tease%20them%20that%20they%20are.%20As%20the%20ad%20goes%2C%20it%20was%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20perfect%3F%20No.%20But%20families%20aren't%20perfect%2C%20and%20every%20relationship%20involves%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Andrew%20and%20me%2C%20sharing%20adult%20time%20with%20our%20kids%20and%20their%20partners%20without%20the%20distraction%20of%20work%20and%20rushing%20was%20wonderful.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20much%20longer%20before%20another%20generation%20joins%20our%20family%20(we%20can't%20wait%20to%20be%20grandparents!)%2C%20but%20babies%20will%20change%20everything.%20Andrew%20and%20I%20really%20appreciated%20this%20time%20as%20a%20group%20of%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20lovely%20to%20observe%20our%20adult%20kids%20interact%20with%20their%20siblings%20and%20their%20partners.%20All%20you%20want%20as%20a%20parent%20is%20happy%2C%20healthy%20children%2C%20and%20to%20see%20them%20all%20happy%20and%20healthy%20basking%20in%20the%20Italian%20sun%20was%20joyful%20beyond%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20kids%20are%20back%20home%20in%20Melbourne%20already%2C%20one%20will%20return%20home%20next%20week%20and%20one%20at%20the%20end%20of%20August.%20When%20we're%20all%20back%20in%20Melbourne%2C%20we'll%20make%20pasta%20and%20reminisce%20about%20our%20wonderful%20Puglian%20holiday.%20That%20time%20when%20we%20all%20got%20gastro!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20bond%20as%20a%20family%20unit%20is%20that%20much%20tighter%20%3A)%20There's%20no%20price%20that%20can%20be%20paid%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-couple-paid-for-adult-kids-to-travel-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722691022000%