rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultitude%20of%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20felt%20dizzy%20when%20she%20stood%20up%2C%20had%20blackouts%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20sleep%20arthritis%2C%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%20Things%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20was%20bedridden.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20her%20studies%20or%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20since%20some%20of%20her%20symptoms%20matched%20with%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20parents%20had%20her%20tested%20for%20it.%20When%20she%20tested%20negative%2C%20the%20doctor%20suggested%20a%20complete%20blood%20checkup%20with%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20thyroid%2C%20diabetes%2C%20iron%2C%20serum%20creatinine%2C%20Vitamin%20B12%2C%20D%2C%20B9%2C%20etc.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20some%20X-rays%20and%20the%20result%20was%20clear%3A%20Snehal%20was%20nutritionally%20deficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20ate%20home-cooked%20vegetarian%20meals%20and%20followed%20a%20healthy%20diet.%20I%20was%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20exercised%20regularly.%20How%20could%20I%20have%20a%20vitamin%20deficiency%3F%20I%20was%20in%20disbelief%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20diagnosis%20shed%20light%20on%20an%20often-overlooked%20aspect%20of%20nutrition%3A%20the%20potential%20for%20deficiency%20even%20in%20seemingly%20healthy%20diets.%20Moreover%2C%20her%20condition%20was%20compounded%20by%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome%20(PCOS)%2C%20a%20hormonal%20disorder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20popping%20more%20than%2010%20pills%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20who%20was%20then%20given%20a%20battery%20of%20medicines%20for%20different%20vitamin%20deficiencies%20and%20advised%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20in%20her%20diet%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20overall%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20buried%20herself%20in%20research%20to%20understand%20which%20foods%20were%20nutrient-dense%20and%20aid%20in%20a%20healthy%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98superfoods%E2%80%99%20she%20found%20at%20this%20time%20was%20microgreens.%20Little%20did%20she%20realise%20then%20that%20she%20would%20be%20launching%20an%20associated%20startup%20with%20her%20classmate%2C%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20four%20years%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20AgriQulture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESnehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20AgriQulture%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayak%20also%20had%20a%20deep%20passion%20for%20nutrition%20and%20wanted%20to%20develop%20a%20product%20that%20could%20make%20nutrition%20available%20to%20people%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditionally%2C%20India%20has%20only%20focused%20on%20protein%2C%20while%20missing%20out%20on%20micronutrients.%20Vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20phytonutrients%20are%20equally%20important%20and%20beneficial%20to%20us.%20We%20generally%20rely%20on%20supplements%20and%20medicines%20to%20get%20these%20nutrients.%20But%20nothing%20beats%20real%20food%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20good%20results%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayak%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20beetroot%20microgreens%2C%20which%20are%20only%20one%20to%20two%20inches%20in%20height%20and%20weigh%2030%20grams%2C%20will%20give%20you%20as%20many%20vitamins%20as%20half%20a%20kilogram%20of%20beetroot.%20These%20tiny%20plants%20pack%20a%20punch%2C%20literally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayak%20says%20that%20microgreens%20contain%20significantly%20more%20nutrients%20than%20mature%20vegetables.%20To%20explain%20the%20benefits%20that%20microgreens%20offer%2C%20Dr%20Akshat%20Chadha%2C%20a%20general%20physician%20with%20expertise%20in%20lifestyle%20medicine%2C%20lists%20their%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20microgreens%20are%20rich%20in%20iron%2C%20Vitamin%20K%2C%20Vitamin%20C%2C%20selenium%2C%20magnesium%2C%20manganese%2C%20antioxidants%2C%20and%20Vitamin%20E.%20They%20are%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20the%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chadha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfog