ompetition%20in%20swimming.%20It%20was%20sometime%20in%202013-14%20and%20we%20threw%20a%20big%20party%20for%20her%20with%20all%20relatives%20and%20friends.%20They%20all%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20her%20and%20wanted%20her%20to%20continue%20and%20achieve%20bigger%20things.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20I%20had%20ever%20seen%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20son%20Anjumon%2C%20his%20voice%20brimming%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20heard%20parents%20speak%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%E2%80%99s%20pleasantly%20surprising%20when%20the%20tables%20are%20turned%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%2062-year-old%20Ranjita%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20tale%20of%20achieving%20her%20dreams%2C%20age%20no%20bar!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20down%20a%20government%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20(BSc)%20in%20agriculture%2C%20Ranjita%20got%20a%20government%20job.%20Post%20marriage%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20a%20nearby%20district%20of%20Jorhat%2C%20where%20she%20continued%20her%20service.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20a%20few%20years%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20PhD%20degree.%20Always%20eager%20to%20learn%2C%20she%20pursued%20a%20course%20in%20computer%20programming%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6mYkQLhNDG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6mYkQLhNDG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView