%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20after%20doing%20self-study%20for%20so%20long%2C%20sitting%20in%20a%20class%20of%201%2C000%20students%20seemed%20impossible.%20We%20decided%20to%20opt%20for%20online%20coaching%2C%20which%20would%20help%20us%20study%20at%20our%20pace%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%202017%2C%20much%20before%20online%20lectures%20were%20the%20norm.%20Using%20online%20lectures%2C%20the%20duo%20prepared%20for%20the%20inter%20exams%20from%20Morena%2C%20and%20cleared%20the%20exam%20on%20the%20first%20attempt%20in%20May%202018.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20eight%20subjects%20split%20into%20two%20groups%20in%20Inter%2C%20and%20while%20some%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20take%20one%20group%E2%80%99s%20exams%20at%20a%20time%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20both%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20all%20CA%20students%20had%20to%20go%20in%20for%20a%20three-year%20articleship%2C%20a%20practical%20training%20at%20a%20CA%20firm.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20siblings%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandini5-min-1722243556.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nandini%20and%20Sachin%20secured%20ranks%20in%20CA%20Final%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandini5-min-1722243556.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandini5-min-1722243556-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandini5-min-1722243556-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandini5-min-1722243556-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsachin-nandi