%22wp-image-358959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20exam%20had%20eight%20subjects%20at%20that%20time%2C%20they%20completed%20their%20first%20revision%20in%20two%20months.%20They%20referred%20to%20The%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20modules%20and%20past%20papers%2C%20and%20took%20some%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20revision%20included%20trying%20to%20solve%20past%20papers%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20an%20idea%20about%20which%20areas%20needed%20more%20focus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20targeted%2010%20days%20for%20two%20subjects%20in%20this%20revision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20they%20attempted%20some%20mock%20test%20papers%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March.%20The%20results%20were%20shocking%2C%20says%20Sachin.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20failed%20in%20a%20few%20papers.%20Even%20in%20other%20subjects%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20result%20we%20wanted.%20We%20were%20shattered%20to%20see%20the%20result%20after%20all%20our%20hard%20work.%20This%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%20to%20secure%20a%20rank%2C%20which%20was%20our%20aim%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20and%20Nandini%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20it%20lightly.%20They%20doubled%20their%20efforts%20and%20spoke%20to%20professors%20about%20what%20was%20lacking.%20The%20professors%20helped%20them%20with%20language%2C%20format%2C%20templates%2C%20and%20paper%20presentations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20also%20helped%20was%20their%20companionship.%20Nandini%20says%20it%20kept%20distractions%20at%20bay%20and%20made%20studying%20an%20enjoyable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20bored%20when%20you%20study%20together.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20study%20buddies%20since%20Class%202.%20We%20helped%20each%20other%20as%20we%20had%20complementary%20skill%20sets.%20We%20would%20teach%20each%20other%20the%20subjects%20we%20were%20strong%20in.%20Sachin%20also%20served%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Study%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358909%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudy%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20they%20were%20better%20prepared.%20While%20the%20exams%20are%20usually%20held%20in%20May%20each%20year%2C%20in%202021%2C%20owing%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20were%20postponed%20to%20July.%20Those%20two%20extra%20months%20served%20as%20a%20major%20boon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20their%20guard%20down%20even%20with%20the%20extra%20time%E2%80%94they%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize.%20They%20did%20another%20revision%20and%20solved%20past%20papers%2C%20revision%20test%20papers%2C%20and%20mock%20test%20papers.%20For%20subjects%20they%20found%20difficult%2C%20like%20SFM%2C%20t